# Walkthrough: RoboLedger v5.1 "Forensic Workbench"

This update marks the transition to a professional, high-density auditing workflow.

## New Features

### 1. Integrated Split-View Audit
The app now supports a side-by-side "Workbench" layout. 
- **Trigger**: Clicking any row in the transaction grid (that has a source PDF).
- **Behavior**: The grid compacts to the left, and a PDF viewer pane slides in on the right. 
- **Benefit**: Zero-friction verification. You can review the bank statement and the ledger entry at the same time.

### 2. AI Audit Hub (v5.1)
The workbench header features the new **Audit Hub**:
- **Google Gemini AI**: High-fidelity, context-aware classification.
- **Local Logic**: Fast, pattern-based matching.
- **Turbo Categorize**: A unified action to process all selected or "Raw" transactions through the chosen AI engine.

### 3. Smart Blob Storage
Transactions are now cryptographically linked to their source file blobs. When you upload a statement, the original file is preserved in memory (accessible via `fileId`) to power the workbench viewer without needing separate downloads.

### 4. Professional Versioning (v5.1)
Updated brand architecture to reflect the v5.1 enterprise-grade status.

