![Forensic Workbench Mockup](file:///C:/Users/asmia/.gemini/antigravity/brain/410a76b2-0025-4cfc-a894-2bba5b8c33e5/forensic_workbench_mockup_1770159549131.png)

## Verification Steps
1. **Import**: Upload an RBC PDF statement.
2. **Review**: Click a transaction row in the grid.
3. **Audit**: Watch the workbench slide out and render the original PDF statement.
4. **Categorize**: Use the Audit Hub to trigger the AI analysis cycle.
